description: Contains detailed data on trademark applications filed or trademark registrations issued by the USPTO to include serial number, registration number, filing date, registration date, goods and services, classification number(s), status code(s), and design search code(s) (no drawings/images) from April 1870 - December 2016. The files are in both CSV and DTA formats and were generated by parsing and converting eXtensible Markup Language (XML) within the zipfiles of the Trademark Daily XML Files (TDXF), applications. https://bulkdata.uspto.gov/data3/trademark/casefile/economics/2016
